image_analysis.description: A photograph showing a narrow hallway or storage area. A white door at the end of the hall has a red sign that reads '24 HOUR VIDEO SURVEILLANCE'. In front of the door and along the right wall are numerous large bags of 'Fafard' brand potting mix and soil. Some bags are stacked on a black rolling utility cart, while others are piled on the carpeted floor. To the left, a portion of a carpeted staircase is visible.
image_analysis.layout: Indoor hallway scene with objects obstructing a doorway.
